---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-base-200 border-t border-base-300 mt-8">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div>
      <div class="text-base-content">
        <p data-lang="en">Pixtitch is an ongoing project by Hiroshi Ohba, exploring the intersection of pixel art and embroidery.</p>
        <p>Pixtitch は、オオバヒロシによる、ピクセルアートと刺繍の間を探るプロジェクトです。</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Drawn to color, sparkle, and believing in what can't be seen. Living in Fukuoka, Japan.</p>
        <p data-lang="ja">色彩やきらめき、目に見えないものを信じることが好きです。福岡で暮らしています。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center mt-4">
      <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
        <p class="text-base-content/70">
          © {currentYear} Pixtitch
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer> 